Subject: [PATCH] an7581: enable DM_MDIO and MDIO CMD by default

Enable DM_MDIO and MDIO CMD in the default config.

Signed-off-by: Christian Marangi <ansuelsmth@gmail.com>
---
 configs/an7581_evb_defconfig | 3 +++
 configs/an7583_evb_defconfig | 4 ++++
 2 files changed, 7 insertions(+)

diff --git a/configs/an7581_evb_defconfig b/configs/an7581_evb_defconfig
index c74247e13db..66c6774214d 100644
--- a/configs/an7581_evb_defconfig
+++ b/configs/an7581_evb_defconfig
@@ -77,5 +77,8 @@ CONFIG_SPI=y
 CONFIG_DM_SPI=y
 CONFIG_SHA512=y
 CONFIG_AIROHA_ETH=y
+CONFIG_DM_MDIO=y
+CONFIG_CMD_MII=y
+CONFIG_CMD_MDIO=y
 CONFIG_MMC_MTK=y
 CONFIG_AIROHA_SNFI_SPI=y
diff --git a/configs/an7583_evb_defconfig b/configs/an7583_evb_defconfig
index 057104b93af..c5a2b615054 100644
--- a/configs/an7583_evb_defconfig
+++ b/configs/an7583_evb_defconfig
@@ -77,5 +77,9 @@ CONFIG_SPI=y
 CONFIG_DM_SPI=y
 CONFIG_SHA512=y
 CONFIG_AIROHA_ETH=y
+CONFIG_DM_MDIO=y
+CONFIG_MDIO_AIROHA=y
+CONFIG_CMD_MII=y
+CONFIG_CMD_MDIO=y
 CONFIG_MMC_MTK=y
 CONFIG_AIROHA_SNFI_SPI=y
